<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT8">
<l>vāṉiṭaip puyalai mālai varaiyiṭaip piraca mīṉṟa</l>
<l>tēṉiṭaik karumpiṉ cāṟṟait tiruviṉai maruvi vāḻār</l>
<l>māṉiṭap piṟavi yantō matikkilar koḷka tantam</l>
<l>ūṉiṭaik kurampai vāḻkkaik kuṟutiyē vēṇṭi ṉārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The clouds in the sky, Māl, juice of sugarcane mixed with honey brought</l>
<l>From honeycombs in the mountains, Splendor – those who don’t live embracing [him],</l>
<l>Alas, they don’t consider [the danger of] human [re]births. Grasp [that]!</l>
<l>They desire the assurance of their [respective] lives in a body [enmeshed] in flesh.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
